data.description: Check out this beautifully landscaped home in Heritage Oaks! This four bedroom, three bath home, features stained concrete floors, granite countertops throughout, and a unique two-sided fireplace that connects the living room to the back patio. The three car garage sits directly next to an additional parking pad, big enough for an RV. It is located in a beautiful neighborhood, only a minute's walk to the neighborhood clubhouse and pool. You have to see this home!
